To restore the HR_Database:
1)Download "HR_Database.bak" file and place it on your c:\ drive.
2)Open Your SQL Server.
3)Open New Query Window.
4)Run the following Script.
5)Refresh Database.
6)Done.
=================================================================
-------------------------------------|
Restore Database HR_Database         |
from disk ='c:\HR_Database.bak';     |
-------------------------------------|
اللي بطلع عنده خطأ بإنشاء الديجرام يستخدم هالكود بالكويري
--------------------------------------|
use HR_Database;                      |
                                      |
EXEC sp_changedbowner 'sa';           |
--------------------------------------|
